
--- The Threat Intelligence Cycle ---

-- The Intelligence Cycle (Full) --

• Requirements and Direction (Planning)
• Collection (Processing)
• Analysis
• Dissemination
• Feedback


-- The Intelligence Cycle (Requirements and Direction (Planning)) --

>> Intelligence Sources <<

• Open-Source Intelligence (OSINT)

  → Dark web, forums, social media
  → Passive recon, vulnerability, and malware databases
  → Public repositories

• Commercial Threat Intelligence

  → Third-party vendors
  → Proprietary subscription-based threat feeds
  → IOCs, malware signatures, attack patterns

• Vendor Reports and Security Research

  → Published reports and whitepapers

• Information Sharing and Analysis Centers (ISACs)

  → Industry groups facilitating threat intelligence sharing: AUTO-ISAC, AVIATION ISAC, WATER ISAC, E-ISAC, SPACE ISAC


